<subSubSection pageId="15" pageNumber="16" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="15.[151,1437,1675,1867]" pageId="15" pageNumber="16">
Remarks.—One of three species with a body length less than 
<quantity box="[810,884,1675,1699]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.7" pageId="15" pageNumber="16" unit="mm" value="37.0">37 mm</quantity>
and wingspan greater than 
<quantity box="[1180,1270,1675,1699]" metricMagnitude="-1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.1" pageId="15" pageNumber="16" unit="mm" value="110.0">110 mm</quantity>
. Body length is about 
<quantity box="[217,291,1707,1731]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.4" pageId="15" pageNumber="16" unit="mm" value="34.0">34 mm</quantity>
and wingspan is about 
<quantity box="[542,630,1707,1731]" metricMagnitude="-1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.22" pageId="15" pageNumber="16" unit="mm" value="122.0">122 mm</quantity>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Distant, W. L." box="[644,786,1707,1731]" pageId="15" pageNumber="16" pagination="103 - 108" refId="ref67756" refString="Distant, W. L. (1881) Descriptions of new genera and species of Rhynchota from Madagascar. Transactions of the Royal Entomological Society of London, 1881, 103 - 108. https: // doi. org / 10.1111 / j. 1365 - 2311.1881. tb 01534. x" type="journal article" year="1881">Distant 1881</bibRefCitation>
). It can be distinguished further from 
<taxonomicName authority="(Karsch, 1890)" baseAuthorityName="Karsch" baseAuthorityYear="1890" box="[1189,1437,1707,1731]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadidae" genus="Pycna" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="15" pageNumber="16" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="rudis">
<emphasis box="[1189,1270,1707,1731]" italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="16">P. rudis</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Karsch, F. A. F." box="[1284,1429,1707,1731]" pageId="15" pageNumber="16" pagination="85 - 130" refId="ref69057" refString="Karsch, F. A. F. (1890) Beitrage zur kenntniss der singcikaden Afrika's und Madagascar's. Berliner Entomologischer Zeitschrift, 35, 85 - 130. https: // doi. org / 10.1002 / mmnd. 18900350107" type="journal article" year="1890">Karsch, 1890</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authority="Amyot &amp; Audinet-Serville, 1843" authorityName="Amyot &amp; Audinet-Serville" authorityYear="1843" box="[198,638,1739,1763]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadidae" genus="Pycna" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="15" pageNumber="16" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="strix">
<emphasis box="[198,273,1740,1763]" italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="16">P. strix</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Amyot, C. J. B. &amp; Audinet-Serville, A." box="[282,638,1739,1763]" pageId="15" pageNumber="16" refId="ref66726" refString="Amyot, C. J. B. &amp; Audinet-Serville, A. (1843) Histoire Naturelle des Insectes. Hemipteres. Deuxime partie. Homopteres. Homoptera Latr. Librairie encyclopedique de Roret, Paris, 675 pp. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 8471" type="book" year="1843">Amyot &amp; Audinet-Serville, 1843</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
by the ground color scutal depression, timbal cover color contrasting the abdominal tergites, and the lack of dense pile on the abdominal tergites.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="15.[151,1437,1675,1867]" pageId="15" pageNumber="16">
Distribution.—The species is only known from 
<collectingCountry box="[750,885,1805,1831]" name="Madagascar" pageId="15" pageNumber="16">Madagascar</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Metcalf, Z. P." box="[903,1073,1805,1831]" pageId="15" pageNumber="16" pagination="1 - 585" refId="ref69829" refString="Metcalf, Z. P. (1963 a) General catalogue of the Homoptera, Fascicle VIII. Cicadoidea. Part 1. Cicadidae. Section I. Tibiceninae. North Carolina State College Contribution, 1502, i-vii + 1 - 585." type="journal article" year="1963">Metcalf 1963a</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Duffels, J. P. &amp; van der Laan, P. A." box="[1087,1431,1805,1832]" pageId="15" pageNumber="16" refId="ref68709" refString="Duffels, J. P. &amp; van der Laan, P. A. (1985) Catalogue of the Cicadoidea (Homoptera, Auchenorhyncha) 1956 - 1980. Series Entomologica 34. Dr. W. Junk Publishers, Dordrect, 414 pp." type="book" year="1985">Duffels &amp; van der Laan 1985</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Sanborn, A. F." box="[151,311,1841,1867]" pageId="15" pageNumber="16" refId="ref70566" refString="Sanborn, A. F. (2013) Catalogue of the Cicadoidea (Hemiptera: Cicadoidea). With contributions to the bibliography by Martin H. Villet. Elsevier / Academic Press, San Diego, 1001 pp. https: // doi. org / 10.1016 / b 978 - 0 - 12 - 416647 - 9.00001 - 2" type="book" year="2013">Sanborn 2013</bibRefCitation>
; 2020).
</paragraph>
